<br>
Going to show an example of chain casting Tears of Marr/ADOI/Icespear (Assuming NO RESISTS, NO CRITS, and NO FOCUS)<br>
<br>
Example :<br>
5 Seconds -Cast Tears of Marr -- 2550 Damage<br>
2.3 Seconds Wait <br>
3.5 Seconds Cast Ancient Destruction of Ice – 1200 Damage<br>
2.3 Seconds Wait<br>
4.0 Seconds Cast Ice Spear of Solist – 1200 Damage<br>
2.3 Seconds Wait<br>
-----------------<br>
14.4 Second total for 4950 Damage or (20625 Damage in 1 Minute) 343.75 DPS<br>
<br>
The Potential DPS for a wizard is considerably higher if we use our level 60 cold buff focus with a 30% damage focus.<br>
<br>
The average of chaining like this should be somewhere in the 300-340 dps range (Thats with crits, focus and resists). Tears of Marr has low aggro as well as ADOI and Ice Spear. <br>
<br>
NOW I'm not saying do this to every mob, because some mobs will eventually get rather upset with you and come after you. But the potential is there. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=554190">Gemlin - 65 Arcanist</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
